des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : hshen@hamptonproducts.com
Amazon Alexa and the Peace by Hampton products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you cleanrobot - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Peace by Hampton products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Peace by Hampton" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Peace by Hampton account in our "Peace by Hampton" app;
(3). You need to have some Peace by Hampton devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Peace by Hampton" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Peace by Hampton" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Peace by Hampton" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Peace by Hampton", and you'll be navigated to Peace by Hampton login page;
(9). Input your Peace by Hampton account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on plug"
“Alexa, turn off plug"
